{"tid":493774,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Google Drive又做想點呀?","createTime":"2017-12-09T01:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T22:14:26.000Z","uid":33883,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8b65fd7ef9c44b207908ac2b29656e44d08a4383","tid":493774,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T01:45:58.000Z","msg":"頭先一click PC上面個Google Drive時, 就彈咗呢個prompt出嚟, click入個prompt度都只叫你裝嘢, 但冇講發生乜事?!<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/kGvcZb/Google_Drive.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FkGvcZb%2FGoogle_Drive.jpg&h=5172b2f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬, 你個Google Drive唔係用嚟backup同sync嘢架咩? 做乜又話會停, 又叫人裝番個&quot;Backup and Sync&quot;, 玩乜撚啫! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又冇人知發生乜事呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6af823968a66f50a1db48c2fd769232be45e1b","tid":493774,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T01:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我d ebook"},{"pid":"06dc0a3447fe2cc3d0b101a8bbf21187bc4d6421","tid":493774,"uid":3835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T01:47:46.000Z","msg":"好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49dd6c808658d2476fffd22beade2ca889c9d32b","tid":493774,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"xp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一早announce左drive要update啦"},{"pid":"1481975aa2c9f1e538b0de4d826e9aebde9e9d8f","tid":493774,"uid":22507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T01:49:59.000Z","msg":"仲有人用xp..."},{"pid":"ab8d51e6bc9811b155c194cf95ef760f8e923614","tid":493774,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score